definition: relevant/to have to do with/coherent (Physics: light etc)
each other/one another/mutually/fret on the neck of a pipa 琵琶[pi2 pa5] (a fret on the soundboard is called a 品[pin3])
appearance/portrait/picture/government minister/(physics) phase/(literary) to appraise (esp. by scrutinizing physical features)/to read sb's fortune (by physiognomy, palmistry etc)
tree trunk/main part of sth/to manage/to work/to do/capable/cadre/to kill (slang)/to fuck (vulgar)
to be irrelevant/to have nothing to do with

sentences.english: Magdalena considered the past an irrelevant encumbrance.
sentences.chinese: 玛格达莱娜把过去看作毫不相干的累赘。

sentences.english: For wedge experiment, using the concept of coherent length, we obtain the condition for emerging interference fringe obviously.
sentences.chinese: 从相干长度的角度，回答了劈尖干涉条纹出现的条件。

sentences.english: Generalized M2 factor of laser beams with amplitude modulations and phase distortion passing through hard-edge apertures.
sentences.chinese: 部分相干光束通过硬边光阑的推广光束传输M2因子。

sentences.english: A new method for prestack coherent noise elimination is put forward here.
sentences.chinese: 本文提出了一种新的叠前相干干扰滤除方法。

sentences.english: At first glance, a cold climate did nothing to foster plague.
sentences.chinese: 在一般人印象中，气候变冷与疾病流行似乎并不相干。

sentences.english: And I believe it is also the principle that is reflected in the norms governing international relations.
sentences.chinese: 我想这也是国际相干准则所争持的“理”。

sentences.english: The wind and snow life, all irrelevant.
sentences.chinese: 风与雪花的人生，各不相干。

sentences.english: Turbulent coherent structures in the outer region of TBL are mainly lateral vortices.
sentences.chinese: 湍流边界层外区的相干结构主要表现为大尺度横向涡。

sentences.english: The dynamical properties of a three level cascade atom interacting with pair coherent state are studied.
sentences.chinese: 研究对相干态与级联三能原子相互作用的动力学特性。

sentences.english: The concept of coherent states is extended o Lie superalgebras.
sentences.chinese: 本文把相干态的概念推广到李超代数的情形。

sentences.english: The wavefront measurement noise and atmospheric coherent length are estimated from the open loop data.
sentences.chinese: 大气相干长度由去除系统噪声的开环数据得到。

sentences.english: It was no more of affinity with my real name than black is of kin to white.
sentences.chinese: 这同我的真姓名不相干，正如黑白不同一样。

sentences.english: The main component of experiment equipment of coherent harmonic radiation in Hefei is optical klystron.
sentences.chinese: 合肥相干谐波辐射实验装置的主体部分是光学速调管。

sentences.english: Optimizing the fidelity of coherent state of quantum teleportation.
sentences.chinese: 优化相干态量子隐形传态的保真度。

sentences.english: The fissions (or fusions) of these localized coherent structures may occur after their interactions.
sentences.chinese: 这些局域相干结构的相互作用存在裂变和聚变现象。

sentences.english: An analysis is made on the characteristics of multimode coherent superposition state light field higher-order squeezing.
sentences.chinese: 研究了多模相干叠加态光场的高次压缩特性。
